Lección 07 Why/because/who
        WH-questions

Why = ¿Por que?
because = porque..
why not = ¿Por que no?

Why are you studying English?
--> because i want to travel
Whi aren't you studyin English 
--> because i want the rest

Is the board black?
No, it isn't 
why not?
because board is white/ it's white

travel: viajar
desear: desear
rest: descanso

---------------------------

Who => ¿Quien?/ ¿Quienes?

Who is painting the hause?
Who's painting the hause?

who are watching the movie (no se puede simpligicar 're)

a) ¿Por qué esta Braian en el banco?
--> Who's Braian in the bank?
b) ¿Porque el está retirando dinero?
--> because he's withdrawing money
c) ¿Quien es esa mujer?
--> Who's that woman
d) Ella es su hermana
--> She's his sister

